Script:

matrix1 = randi(10, 4, 4);
matrix2 = randi(10, 4, 4);

addition_result = matrix1 + matrix2;

subtraction_result = matrix1 - matrix2;


disp("Matrix 1:");
disp(matrix1);

disp("Matrix 2:");
disp(matrix2);

disp("Addition Result:");
disp(addition_result);

disp("Subtraction Result:");
disp(subtraction_result);

Output:

Matrix 1:
