    10     1    10     5
     2     3     2     9
    10     6    10     2

Matrix 2:
     5     7     7     7
    10     1     8     2
     8     9     8     8
    10    10     4     1

Addition Result:
    14    14    17    17
    20     2    18     7
    10    12    10    17
    20    16    14     3

Subtraction Result:
     4     0     3     3
     0     0     2     3
    -6    -6    -6     1
     0    -4     6     1

